column4: NSLOCTEXT("[620D80E542EA7EE0047E1985BD1AD9AF]", "76D19B2043F4A6ABE2E7358ADA306A83", "He who seeks my help, the time has come! I give you the blessings of my wings!")
NSLOCTEXT("[620D80E542EA7EE0047E1985BD1AD9AF]", "DC7E667B4EC0857888A860A52D61EF79", "What was that? The light is gone. There\'s nothing else here. That means it\'s above?!")
